videos.description: Kentucky's Nick Richards follows the missed jumper and throws down the dunk as the shot clock expires.
videos.headline: Richards slams home the putback dunk

videos.description: Tennessee's John Fulkerson runs the pick-and-roll to perfection as he gets the open dunk off the feed from Lamonte Tuner.
videos.headline: Fulkerson with the emphatic slam off the pick-and-roll

videos.description: Reid Travis hits a last second 3-pointer to cut the deficit for Kentucky to 2 points at the half.
videos.headline: Travis drains the 3 before the halftime buzzer

videos.description: PJ Washington uses a powerful move in the post to get by his initial defender then dunks over the next.
videos.headline: Washington posterizes defender in the paint

videos.description: Reid Travis gets the steal and Keldon Johnson does the rest as he takes the ball all the way for the fast-break dunk.
videos.headline: Johnson storms down the court for monster dunk

videos.description: Tennessee completes a late game comeback to take the lead as Grant Williams nails a 3-pointer in the corner to put them up 75-74.
videos.headline: Tennessee bench explodes as Williams hits 3
